OL,3,CEx-PhD student, 47, jailed in
OL,4,C'landmark' case over plot to commit FGM
OL,6,FA former PhD student has been jailed
OL,7,Fin a "landmark" case after becoming
OL,8,Fthe first person to be convicted of
OL,9,Fconspiracy to commit female genital
OL,10,Fmutilation (FGM) in England and Wales.
OL,12,FEmad Kaky, 47, was living in
OL,13,FNottingham when he arranged for a
OL,14,Fyoung girl to travel from the UK to
OL,15,FIraq where he had organised for her to
OL,16,Fbe subjected to FGM and forced into an
OL,17,Farranged marriage.
