OL,3,CEx-PhD student, 47, jailed in
OL,4,C'landmark' case over plot to commit FGM
OL,6,FA witness uncovered Kaky's plans
OL,7,Fbefore the procedure never took place
OL,8,Fand arranged for the child to get back
OL,9,Fto the UK.
OL,11,FKaky, who now lives in Swansea, was
OL,12,Ffound guilty of the offence has
OL,13,Fsentenced to four-and-a-half years in
OL,14,Fprison at Nottingham Crown Court.
OL,16,FHe was also found guilty of one count
OL,17,Fof forced marriage.
OL,19,FWhen challenged in court, Kaky said
OL,20,Fforced marriage and FGM were "normal".
