OL,6,F"The law is clear that there is no
OL,7,Fplace for this unacceptable practice
OL,8,Fin society, and the Crown Prosecution
OL,9,FService, police, and other law
OL,10,Fenforcement agencies will work
OL,11,Ftogether to bring perpetrators to
OL,12,Fjustice.
OL,14,F"This has been a landmark prosecution,
OL,15,Fnot just because it is the first
OL,16,Fconviction of its kind, but for the
OL,17,Fmessage it sends to people who may be
OL,18,Fvulnerable to this horrific form of
OL,19,Fabuse.
