OL,6,F"Where there is evidence that people
OL,7,Fhave plotted to commit these offences,
OL,8,Fthey face prosecution, whether or not
OL,9,Fthey succeed."
OL,11,FThis is the third FMG-related
OL,12,Fconviction in British history.
OL,14,FWhat is FGM?
OL,16,FFGM, or female genital mutilation, is
OL,17,Fa practice where external female
OL,18,Fgenitalia is removed or damaged for
OL,19,Fnon-medical reasons. It has been
OL,20,Fillegal in the UK since 1985.
