OL,6,FThere are four different types of FGM,
OL,7,Franging from the removal of the
OL,8,Fclitoris (Type 1) to the creation of a
OL,9,Fseal to narrow the vaginal opening
OL,10,F(Type 3). All other harmful procedures
OL,11,Fto the genitals are classed as Type 4.
OL,13,FAll forms of FMG are dangerous and can
OL,14,Flead to life-changing injuries or even
OL,15,Fdeath.
OL,17,FAccording to UNICEF data, over 230
OL,18,Fmillion girls and women currently
OL,19,Fliving have undergone FGM in the 30
OL,20,Fcountries where it is commonly
OL,21,Fpractised.
